product.title: Harajuku Japanese Fish Konnichiwa Poster Unisex Hoodie
product.body_html:
• Description
  • FAQ
  • Shipping

  • Do you love Japanese-themed tops?

    Then you don't want to miss out on this awesome Japanese-themed hoodie featuring an illustration of a fish poster on the back and a fish icon on the front. With a classic look, this high-quality tee is great to add some fun to your wardrobe. Each hoodie is sold separately.

    Measurements are shown below. We recommend comparing the measurements to a hoodie that fits to avoid any disappointment. If in doubt, just go one size up because a larger hoodie is always comfy to wear!

    Size (inches) S M L XL XXL XXXL
    Bust 35 39 41 43 44 48
    Length 25 25 26 27 28 27
    Sleeve 23 23 23 24 24 25
                 
    Size (cm) S M L XL XXL XXXL
    Bust 90 96 102 108 114 120
    Length 64 66 68 70 72 74
    Sleeve 58 59 60 61 62 63


    Features

    ✨ Made from 80% premium polyester microfiber & 20% premium soft cotton
    ✨ Promotes warmth, comfort, and durability

    Measurements may be off by 1-5cm for rounding up to a whole number.

    If you are interested in more items like this, please check out our website www.kawaiies.com

  • Please follow the washing labels when cleaning the garment:

     Max temperature 30c, or cold water. Reverse the garment to protect the print.

     Do not bleach

     Dry by the sun or hang it to dry. 

     Dry cleaning

     

  • FREE Tracked Shipping to the United States, Canada, United Kingdom, Australia, New Zealand, Germany, Spain, France, Italy, Austria, Netherlands, and many more. Find out more here: Shipping Policy.

    Packaging time: 1-3 Business days

    Shipping time: Est 5-30 Business days
